main event: A witness in Warrington, Pennsylvania observed a round, silver-colored object that traveled in a straight line and disappeared and reappeared during the observation.
interesting points: The object was observed for about 5 minutes.
The object made a rising, metallic sound.
The witness stated the description was consistent with an aircraft, but the missing sound was related to the observation of a silent UFO.
The object appeared quite large, covering about 3/4 of the witness's field of view.
The witness did not provide an estimate of the object's speed or distance, but indicated it moved behind something at one point during the sighting.
